  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/latest_news/\u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca-\u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca-\u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0db8-\u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1-\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca-\u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca/1-618919",
  "time_ut": 1661750145,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0db8 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An assurance from Harsha about the newly assumed chairmanship",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Harsha De Silva, Colombo District Member of Samagi Jana Balawega said that he accepts the position of Chairman of the Finance Committee and fulfills its responsibilities to the best of his ability.",
        "Mr. Anura Priyadarshana Yapa, the former chairman of the said committee, also managed the position of chairman of the said committee well with his best efforts and for that he thanked him as the new chairman.",
        "Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera said to look into the procurement of fuel and coal and Mr. Harsha de Silva said that the Finance Committee has full powers and will act immediately to fulfill the minister's request.",
        "Investigate and appoint a separate committee for this purpose. Make procurement from the committee."
      ],
